1. Общая картина — должны быть true, false и NULL:

SELECT is_aligned_tran, count(*) 
FROM ice_baby.core_flow_ing_raw.raw_bptransaction_test
GROUP BY is_aligned_tran

2. Тендеры — должны быть НЕ только NULL:

SELECT is_aligned_tran, count(*) 
FROM ice_baby.core_flow_ing_raw.raw_bptender_test
GROUP BY is_aligned_tran

3. Типы 11xx/13xx/16xx — должны быть NULL, а не false:

SELECT transactiontypecode, is_aligned_tran, count(*) as cnt
FROM ice_baby.core_flow_ing_raw.raw_bptransaction_test
WHERE transactiontypecode IN ('1101','1103','1107','1108','1301','1601')
GROUP BY transactiontypecode, is_aligned_tran

4. Типы 1001-1003 — должны быть в основном true:

SELECT transactiontypecode, is_aligned_tran, count(*) as cnt
FROM ice_baby.core_flow_ing_raw.raw_bptransaction_test
WHERE transactiontypecode IN ('1001','1002','1003')
GROUP BY transactiontypecode, is_aligned_tran
